title: Grateful Dead Live at Rec Hall, Penn State U on 1980-05-06
description: Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Peggy-O, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Loser, Far From Me, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Althea-> Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Feel Like A Stranger-> He's Gone-> The Other One-> Drums-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around-> Johnny B. Goode, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text: ugh! Nice to have these recordings, but this one is hardly worth the effort, especially when a m uch better one is available!
my uncle taped this show with a walkman, literally.  this might really be his recording.
